Friday night 
June 30th
Outside Hotel Thermal 
Karlovy Vary
Czech Republic 
This is a free concert 
No ticket required
Last show of the tour 
For all of those asking “ when will you play in …( add European City) 
This gig is in Central Europe 
Get off your ass, get on a bus, a train , a plane or your car.
Deal with the opportunity that is right in front of you.
Karlovy Vary is an historically important and beautiful spa town, who’s previous guests include 
Beethoven…
Chopin…
Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart…
Come on, what an opportunity to expand your world and have an adventure.
The last time we played Europe was 2017. It doesn’t come around often.
The concert is free…
No ticket required,
No bullshit registration rubbish.
You turn up, you see the show.
We are shooting the #lastbreath documentary.
Be one of the cool kids that can say “ I was there” .
Don’t miss this show…

23 shows.
4 countries.
What a beautiful cast & crew.
